App Overview

Build a cross-platform native mobile fashion inspiration app using Expo + React Native that helps users discover swaggy, stylish outfit ideas. The app should showcase curated fashion looks, outfit combinations, and styling inspiration using a public fashion-related API or open image/content source.

The app must work seamlessly on iOS, Android, and Web, with a clean UI, smooth navigation, and modern styling. It should be structured for easy deployment to Vercel for the web version and Expo for mobile builds.

Technical Requirements

Framework: Expo (React Native)

Language: TypeScript

Routing: Expo Router

Styling: NativeWind (Tailwind CSS for React Native) or StyleSheet

Data Fetching: fetch or axios

State Management: React Hooks (useState, useEffect)

Environment Variables: Expo-compatible (EXPO_PUBLIC_*)

Web Compatibility: Must run with expo start --web

Deployment Target: Vercel

