Search outfits by keyword (e.g., â€œbaggy jeansâ€, â€œoversized hoodieâ€)

Optional mood-based inspiration (minimal, bold, edgy)

Favorites (Optional)

Save favorite outfits locally using AsyncStorage

API Integration

Use a free, open fashion or image API to power outfit inspiration.

Recommended Options:

Option 1: Unsplash API (Fashion-based image search)

Base URL: https://api.unsplash.com/

Endpoint: /search/photos

Query examples: streetwear outfit, fashion style, urban fashion

Requires free API key (use env variable)

Option 2: Pexels API (Alternative)

Fashion & outfit photography

Free developer access

Good for lifestyle & streetwear images

If API keys are required, store them in:

process.env.EXPO_PUBLIC_UNSPLASH_KEY

Styling & UI Guidelines

Mobile-first design

Clean, bold typography

Dark-mode inspired aesthetic preferred

High-contrast outfit cards

Rounded edges, smooth shadows

Swipe-friendly UI

Use Tailwind utility classes if NativeWind is enabled

